data.meta_description: Anthony Dobbins is an American-Italian professional basketball coach and former player who is an assistant coach for the Boston Celtics of the National Basketball Association (NBA).
data.text:
Anthony Dobbins is an American-Italian professional basketball coach and former player who is an assistant coach for the Boston Celtics of the National Basketball Association (NBA).
